mesa
------------------------------------------
X11 OpenGL libraries

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  libX11_6-1.1.5-1
  libXext6-1.0.4-1
  libXm2-0.95.0-2
  libXt6-1.0.5-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.4.2-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  gcc-g++-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.23a-2
  sed-4.1.5-2
  glproto-1.4.9-1

Canonical website:
  http://mesa3d.org/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/mesa3d/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mesa-7.2-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mesa-7.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mesa-7.2-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL-devel-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL1-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU-devel-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU1-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw-devel-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw1-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOSMesa-devel-7.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOSMesa7-7.2-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

